此站於1918年8月1日啟用<ref name="NYTimes Opening">{{cite web|title=New Subway Lines Will Open Tonight: Ceremonies to Mark Through Service on 7th and Lexington Links of System|url=http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=940CE4DE1739E13ABC4953DFBE668383609EDE|website=[[The_New_York_Times|nytimes.com]]|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=30 June 2015|date=August 1, 1918|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305154143/http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=940CE4DE1739E13ABC4953DFBE668383609EDE|dead-url=no}}</ref>，令此站成為IRT佩勒姆線上最古老的車站。設有兩個[[島式月台|島式月台]]和三條軌道，中央軌道用中平日尖峰時段的特快服務。平日尖峰時段，有一至兩班6號線列車以此站為總站<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/pdf/t6cur.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-02-21 |archive-date=2017-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170316095902/http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/pdf/t6cur.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
